Name: Brick Breaker Ultimate
About the game: Brick Breaker Ultimate [/] is a 'Brick Breaker' style game where you aim to make the best score. To do this, simply break the bricks with your balls that you can recover during your game. It is an arcade-style game that allows you to relax while watching a video or to entertain yourself while loading another game for example.
